Nollywood actor and winner of Big Brother Africa Season 5 reality TV show, Uti Nwachukwu, has identified 2020 Big Brother Naija Lockdown BBNaija housemate, Prince, as the most intelligent and filled with wisdom in the reality show. According to Nwachukwu, Prince needs to be appreciated with the most accolades in the house because of his intelligence. Nwachukwu stated this in a tweet via his official Twitter account at the weekend. He tweeted: “I honestly think that when it comes to deep and Real Intelligence mixed with wisdom in that #Bbnaija house, PRINCE should definitely be given more, if not the most accolades. “We need to appreciate him a whole lot more the guy yans like an IGWE.” Meanwhile, evicted Big Brother Naija, BBNaija housemate, Ka3na, has said that she wants Prince to win the ‘Lockdown’ edition of the reality show because he is intelligent and multi-talented. Ka3na said: “I am rooting for all my fellow housemates to win, but most especially I want Prince to win, he is intelligent and multi-talented whatever he sets his mind to do he achieves them.” <img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-832726" src="https://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/uti-tweet.jpg" alt="" width="584" height="225" srcset="https://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/uti-tweet.jpg 584w, https://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/uti-tweet-300x116.jpg 300w" sizes="(max-width: 584px) 100vw, 584px">